            <ID>CHART_RADIO</ID> 
            <SourceID>DARK_STAR</SourceID> 
            <RumorName>Chert's Message</RumorName> 
            <Text>Chert radioed me about a strange star that suddenly appeared in an otherwise empty patch of space 2,700 lightyears away. It has a strange luminosity profile - the star itself is nearly dead in the visible range, though the corona could belong to a regular star. Riebeck thinks its sudden appearance may be connected to the Nomai.</Text> 
        </RumorFact>
